### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Lista turni
GET {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Turni odierni
GET {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/oggi
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crea turno
POST {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task": "Pulizia cucina",
  "cadenzaGiorni": 14,
  "assegnatario": "{{idUtente}}",
  "rotazioneTurno": false
}

### Dettaglio turno
GET {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/{{idTurno}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Modifica turno
PUT {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/{{idTurno}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task": "Pulizia cucina e bagno",
  "cadenzaGiorni": 14,
  "rotazioneTurno": false
}

### Assegna turno
PUT {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/{{idTurno}}/assegna
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idUtente": "{{idUtente}}"
}

### Toggle rotazione
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/{{idTurno}}/rotazione
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Completa turno
POST {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/{{idTurno}}/completa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Elimina turno
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/turni/{{idTurno}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
